KOMATIPOORT &#8211; The N4 between Komatipoort and Hectorspruit is closed due to an accident between a truck and Sports Utility Vehicle (SUV) on Tuesday.Three of the occupants of the SUV have been fatally injured while two more have sustained serious injuries.According to traffic spokesperson, Moeti Mmusi, emergency services are awaiting a chopper that will transport the two injured.The driver of the truck sustained no injuries.&#8220;Due to the nature of their injuries they have to be airlifted to the nearest hospital,&#8221; he said.Motorists coming to and from Komatipoort are urged to use Tenbosch Road as an alternative road.According to Mmusi, the cause of the accident is unclear.&#8220;The police are investigating,&#8221; he said.